7284
04:44:22.771 --> 04:44:23.331
1

7285
04:44:23.891 --> 04:44:24.771
contra

7286
04:44:24.771 --> 04:44:25.252
6.

7287
04:44:26.417 --> 04:44:27.697
Billy Bones

7288
04:44:27.697 --> 04:44:30.977
